<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-front-of">in front (of)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在 (…) 前面；在 (…) 面前：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He drove straight into the car in front.
他一下子撞上了前面的车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should be brave in front of difficulties.
我们应该勇敢面对困难。</p><footer>2008 辽宁书面表达</footer></div></div>